Project Licensing
=================

This repository contains multiple components with different licenses.

1. embedded_linux_audit agent
-----------------------------

The `embedded_linux_audit` agent program is licensed under the
GNU General Public License, version 3 or (at your option) any later
version.

This applies to the agent and its associated source/build material,
including files under:

- `agent/`
- `compat/` (except where a file states otherwise)
- `tests/agent/`
- `tests/compile_release_binaries_locally.sh`
- `Makefile`
- `.github/workflows/release-cross-static.yml`
- documentation describing the agent CLI under `docs/`

See `COPYING` for the full GPL-3.0-or-later license text.

2. API helper and repository glue
---------------------------------

The Node.js helper API and other repository files not covered above are
licensed under the MIT License.

This includes, for example:

- `api/agent/`
- top-level repository metadata unless otherwise noted

See `LICENSE.api` for the full MIT license text.

