- Git submodules and bundled third-party code under `third_party/` remain
  under their own respective licenses.

Notable third-party license notices include:

- `third_party/libcsv` — GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1
  (`third_party/libcsv/COPYING`)
- `third_party/json-c` — MIT License (`third_party/json-c/COPYING`)
- `third_party/curl` — curl license / ISC-style permissive license
