- `third_party/openssl` — Apache License 2.0
  (`third_party/openssl/LICENSE.txt`)
- `third_party/u-boot` — GNU General Public License v2
  (`third_party/u-boot/COPYING`)
- `third_party/libubootenv` — LGPL-2.1-or-later, with additional notices in
